        "content": "### GitHub Pages & RUM\n[→ Full Dashboard](https://geu80787.apps.dynatrace.com/ui/apps/dynatrace.dashboards/dashboard/a20a6def-bbb5-46da-a0c9-1b7e2566e4af)"
